	src/netconsole.c, src/player.c, src/player.h: Fix compiler warnings
	for grubby:   - Mark some functions as static.	  - Give some
	function prototypes parameter lists.  (If you just say	    "void
	foo();" that's not a parameter list - it can match any function.   
